snippet.title: Washout Spire: Free Indie Platformer
snippet.description:
Playthrough of the indie horror game "Washout Spire".
Found on Itch.io at:
https://june-flower.itch.io/washout-spire

Thank you for stopping by. If you enjoyed the video, please like and subscribe. I produce new videos often and would love to take requests. If you have a game you would like to see archived contact me at thevideogameanthologist@gmail.com. I will try my best to play your requests. Look forward to hearing from you!
